John C. Fortson

Age : 49Public asset : 2,197,846 USDLinked companies :  Ingevity Corp 





Summary 



Mr. John C. Fortson is Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Executive VP at Ingevity Corp.He is on the Board of Directors at USO of Illinois. Mr. Fortson was previously employed as CFO, Treasurer, VP & Head-Investor Relations by AAR Corp., Treasurer & Vice President by AAR Airlift Group, Inc., and a Trustee by Ravinia Festival Association.He received his undergraduate degree from US Military Academy and an MBA from The Fuqua School of Business.



