Executive Summary
John Fortson was named CFO of Ingevity in October 2015. Fortson came to Ingevity from AAR Corporation, a leading global aviation and aerospace company, where he served as Vice President, CFO, and Treasurer. Prior to joining AAR in 2013, he held a number of leadership positions with Bank of America Merrill Lynch, including Managing Dire 
